---
// CTABanner.astro
---
<section class="relative py-24 bg-slate-900 border-y border-white/10 overflow-hidden">
  
  <!-- Subtle gradient lines -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 inset-x-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/20 to-transparent"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 inset-x-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/20 to-transparent"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 mb-8 backdrop-blur-sm">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-amber-500"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/><path d="M14.05 2a9 9 0 0 1 8 7.94"/><path d="M14.05 6A5 5 0 0 1 18 10"/></svg>
      <span class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-300">Free Lead Gen Audit &mdash; No Obligation</span>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white leading-[1.1] mb-6 tracking-tight">
      If Calls Are Being Missed,<br/>
      <span class="text-amber-500 mt-2 block">They Get Captured.</span>
    </h2>

    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-300 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      Book a free strategy call with Bob Rutledge. He'll review your current campaigns, your website, and your call handling &mdash; and show you exactly where leads are leaking out of your pipeline.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-10">
      <a href="https://calendar.app.google/RUTjw3N7Afe95Tkk8" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-10 py-5 bg-amber-500 hover:bg-amber-600 text-[#020617] font-black rounded-full text-lg shadow-2xl shadow-amber-500/20 transition-transform hover:scale-95 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 group">
        Book a Time to Talk
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
      <a href="tel:+12517650333" class="w-full sm:w-auto px-10 py-5 border-2 border-white/30 text-white hover:border-white/60 font-bold rounded-full text-lg transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
        +1 (251) 765-0333
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:gap-6 text-[10px] md:text-xs text-white/40 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider">
      <span>✓ No long-term contracts</span>
      <span class="hidden sm:block opacity-50">&bull;</span>
      <span>✓ 25+ years PPC experience</span>
      <span class="hidden sm:block opacity-50">&bull;</span>
      <span>✓ Built exclusively for contractors</span>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
